{"tid":1481852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日817多倫多發生嘅事","createTime":"2019-08-18T01:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:38:17.000Z","uid":287572,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d5cbed83004a3214cfc1f90786ef70a71878ca64","tid":1481852,"uid":287572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:13:06.000Z","msg":"我想介紹下今日係多倫多集會嘅地點。<br />\n<br />\n今日我哋係多倫多嘅Old City Hall 出面集會，而出面有一個記念一戰、二戰同韓戰，為咗保護加拿大嘅自由同人民嘅士兵的和平記念碑。令人憤怒嘅係，今日竟然有一班大陸夠企咗係上面，攞住中國國旗唱中國國歌。<br />\n<br />\n呢種行為係非常之侮辱為咗加拿大而犧牲嘅士兵。企係上面已經係好唔尊重，仲要係上面唱他國國歌，揮他國國旗，簡直令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n小弟希望咁多位巴絲打可以幫手推件事上去，令更多人知道，大陸狗點樣令自己係國外蒙羞。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwQ9NZ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwQ9NZ3.jpg&h=54675029&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6719ab46b037f797d0e860249e88841c3151271c","tid":1481852,"uid":287572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:20:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e8c6049d482cd3bc169fdd5bfeafcfb62f7e43d8","tid":1481852,"uid":287572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:20:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"19bf096cacfbe80853f7bbb9b6eac4f92eadade6","tid":1481852,"uid":287572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:20:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"256985140cd61d29a45954ba92ec887c3c61a3f2","tid":1481852,"uid":153488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:22:15.000Z","msg":"又柒出國際，推"},{"pid":"04ce7f667aaeeb38b0215c7e73a61b960a1bf2fb","tid":1481852,"uid":287572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:22:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5b9627f884086a6d9a64342e97f44c13b20e60c3","tid":1481852,"uid":153488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:24:00.000Z","msg":"推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i